oracle.kubernetes.operator.helpers

Class LifeCycleHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.kubernetes.operator.helpers.LifeCycleHelper

  • public class LifeCycleHelper
extends Object
    This helper class uses the domain resource that the customer configured to calculate the effective configuration for the servers and clusters in the domain.

      • getEffectiveDomainConfig

        public DomainConfig getEffectiveDomainConfig(Domain domain,
                                             Set<String> servers,
                                             Map<String,Set<String>> clusters)
        Get the effective configurations of the clusters and servers in this domain.
        Parameters:
        domain - the domain that the customer configured
        servers - the names of the non-clustered servers that are actually configured for this domain
        clusters - the clusters that are actually configured for this domain (the map keys are cluster name,s the map values are sets of the names of the servers in each cluster)
        Returns:
        a the effective configurations of the clusters and servers
